    {
      "id": "34b500d0_9ee0a0ca",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/dcaegen2-services/components/dcae-pmsh/resources/config/application.json",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 1,
      "message": "> We are using configMap to populate PMSH Monitoring policy to Concul via Consul Loader Image in Init-Container. which is making use of Consul Loader Image to put data against same dcae-pmsh parent Key with \"policy\" as key which will keep data in nested fashion with relevent keys and at moment we are querying data with \"policy\" key in PMSH Code base this help us with zero code update impact on PMSH.\n> Also if we dont provide a explict key, values in consul will get overridden against same key, after having policy as key below is data in consul.\n\n> curl --location --request GET 'http://xx.xx.xx.xx:10000/service_component_all/dcae-pmsh'\n{\n   \"config\":{\n    },\n   \"policy\":{\n      \"subscription\":{}\n    },\n}",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 6004,
        "name": "Ajay Deep Singh",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "ajay.deep.singh@est.tech",
        "username": "ajay_dp001"
      },
      "updated": "2021-04-01 15:23:06.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "0be578c3_9198589d",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
